# URL: https://www.gentoo.org/support/news-items/2022-07-29-pipewire-sound-server.html

# Choice 1: Pipewire
# (pipewire-alsa: Install ALSA plugin, similar to media-plugins/alsa-plugins's)
# media-video/pipewire sound-server pipewire-alsa
# media-sound/pulseaudio -daemon
# */* pipewire pulseaudio

# Choice 2: Pulse audio
media-video/pipewire -sound-server
media-sound/pulseaudio daemon
*/* -pipewire pulseaudio

# Global config
# extra: The Portage package manager requires the extra USE flag to be active
# whenever the ffmpeg USE flag is enabled for media-video/pipewire. Fixes: The
# following REQUIRED_USE flag constraints are unsatisfied: ffmpeg? ( extra )
media-video/pipewire extra
